Steps to add apps
1. C:\Users\Rain\django\mysite> python manage.py startapp weather
2. settings.py, INSTALLED_APPS, add 'weather'
3. create templates\weather\weather.html
4. In mysite\urls.py, add in urlpatterns, path('', include('weather.urls'))
5. copy from settings\urls to weather\urls, keep the essential part
6. create function index in views.py
	- register on openweathermap to get an API
7. Add in models.py
8. makemigrations
9. migration


=========================================
sqlite command
sqlite3 db.sqlite3
.tables
select * from weather_city;
delete from weather_city where id=5;
.exit
